ALL: No.
"Snake Inhalers." Yeah?

11:28.339 --> 11:29.776
Nope.
"Spanish Inquisition"?

11:29.819 --> 11:31.865
No, that's...
"Saint Ignatius"?

11:31.908 --> 11:32.779
What?
How have you
made it this far?

11:32.822 --> 11:34.171
"Spare Bedroom"?
No.

11:34.215 --> 11:35.390
"Spanakopita"?

11:35.433 --> 11:36.739
Here.
I'm nearsighted, too.

11:38.480 --> 11:42.092
Oh, it's "Space Invaders."

11:42.136 --> 11:43.659
That makes sense.

11:43.703 --> 11:45.792
So you're finally admitting
to yourself that you need
glasses?

11:45.835 --> 11:48.751
I've always known!
I can't believe
you all knew

11:48.795 --> 11:49.839
and never cared enough
to tell me.

11:51.058 --> 11:52.146
Why?

11:52.189 --> 11:53.800
I'll get us each
a new pair.

11:53.843 --> 11:56.324
ADULT ADAM: Yep, our team
was ready to end
our losing streak,

11:56.367 --> 11:59.240
and Erica was determined
to win over Geoff's dad.

11:59.283 --> 12:02.591
Thank you, Dr. Schwartz, for
joining us today in your home.

12:02.634 --> 12:05.899
