You bet.

12:34.014 --> 12:36.407
Erica's a great influence
on me.

12:36.451 --> 12:37.539
Are you drinking a beer?

12:37.582 --> 12:39.584
Moving on.

12:39.628 --> 12:42.413
Look. Last week,
she took me mini golfing
for half-price Tuesdays.

12:42.457 --> 12:43.675
But Tuesday's a school day.

12:43.719 --> 12:44.807
Moving on.

12:44.851 --> 12:46.766
See, Erica's
really thoughtful, Dad.

12:46.809 --> 12:47.854
She threw me
a surprise party,

12:47.897 --> 12:49.464
and it was
the best night of my life.

12:49.507 --> 12:50.813
Is that my living room?

12:50.857 --> 12:53.729
Did you throw a party
when I was in Miami?

12:53.773 --> 12:54.861
Erica,
please take over again.

12:54.904 --> 12:56.688
No! I've had enough.

12:56.732 --> 12:57.951
This just confirms
what I already knew.

