13:04.305 --> 13:07.221
our team's bigMajor League
plan was coming together.

13:07.264 --> 13:09.049
How's it going, Coach?

13:09.092 --> 13:11.312
Are we gonna win
at sucking or what?

13:11.355 --> 13:12.748
Got my worst men
on it, sir.

13:15.707 --> 13:17.187
Strike!
Three, three!

13:18.710 --> 13:20.016
Yes!

13:20.060 --> 13:23.106
Two down, two down.
Play's at second.

13:23.150 --> 13:25.892
They can play
and know the lingo.

13:25.935 --> 13:27.110
