13:30.722 --> 13:32.550
Unless we
change the schedule.

13:32.594 --> 13:34.335
We have to play
Meadowbrook High?

13:34.378 --> 13:35.205
They're the best team
in the city.

13:35.249 --> 13:36.859
This is bad.

13:36.903 --> 13:39.079
Ball knows we know
he's Major Leagueingus

13:39.122 --> 13:40.776
and that we're
